OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FVariable cloud and patchy
OL,6,Frain for much of the day, with
OL,7,Foccasional bright or sunny intervals
OL,8,Fand temperatures slightly higher than
OL,9,FWednesday. Breezy conditions for
OL,10,Fcoastal areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday
OL,13,Fbrings sunny spells and scattered
OL,14,Fshowers. Confidence lowers into the
OL,15,Fweekend, though rain or showers are
OL,16,Flikely on Saturday at some point.
OL,17,FSunday appears drier, with occasional
OL,18,Fsunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
